# 🧭 SVELTE 5 PROJECT & CODE STANDARDS

---

## 📁 Folder Structure – Feature-Based (Svelte 5 / SvelteKit)
```
src/
├── features/
│   └── [feature-name]/
│       ├── components/         # "Dumb" UI components – presentational only
│       │   └── component-name/
│       │       ├── component-name.svelte
│       │       ├── component-name.module.scss (optional)
│       │       └── index.ts
│       ├── containers/         # "Smart" components – orchestrate state, routing, API
│       │   └── container-name/
│       │       ├── container-name.svelte
│       │       └── index.ts
│       ├── services.svelte.ts  # Business logic (stores, API clients, pure functions)
│       ├── types.ts            # TypeScript interfaces/types
│       ├── analytics.ts        # Analytics helpers
│       └── index.ts            # Public API (re-exports)
├── shared/
│   ├── components/             # Generic, reusable UI
│   │   └── component-name/
│   │       ├── component-name.svelte
│   │       ├── component-name.module.scss (optional)
│   │       └── index.ts
│   ├── stores/*                # Global stores (only when cross-feature)
│   ├── utils/*                 # Pure utilities (e.g., cn, formatters)
│   └── styles/*                # Global styles or Tailwind config
```

---

## 📦 Public API Example
```ts
// features/[feature]/index.ts
export * as someFeatureService from './services.svelte';
export { default as SomeFeatureContainer } from './containers/some-feature-container';
export { default as SomeComponent } from './components/some-component';
export * from './types';
```
- UI inside `shared/components` **must stay generic** — no feature imports.  
- Features remain **self-contained and composable**.

---

## 🧩 Component Structure

**Component Structure in /features/[feature]/components/**
```
component-name/
├── component-name.svelte
├── component-name.module.scss (optional, if Tailwind cannot express the style)
└── index.ts
```

**Component Structure in /features/[feature]/containers/**
```
container-name/
├── container-name.svelte
└── index.ts
```

**Component index.ts Example:**
```ts
// components/component-name/index.ts
export { default } from './component-name.svelte';
```

**Container index.ts Example:**
```ts
// containers/container-name/index.ts
export { default } from './container-name.svelte';
```

